snippet.title: Squid Game: Season 2 | You’re Invited | Netflix
snippet.description:
You're invited to get back in the game.

Season 2 on December 26, 2024.

Only on Netflix.

More Info on Squid Game Season 2:
Three years after winning Squid Game, Player 456 gave up going to the states and comes back with a new resolution in his mind. Gi-hun once again dives into the mysterious survival game, starting another life-or-death game with new participants gathered to win the prize of 45.6 billion won.

Director Hwang Dong-hyuk, who made history at the 74th Primetime Emmys® becoming the first Asian to win Outstanding Directing for a Drama Series, once again helms the series as director, writer, and producer. Lee Jung-jae, Lee Byung-hun, Wi Ha-jun, and Gong Yoo reprise their roles from Season 1 with an impeccable list of new cast members including Yim Si-wan, Kang Ha-neul, Park Gyu-young, Lee Jin-uk, Park Sung-hoon, Yang Dong-geun, Kang Ae-sim, Lee David, Choi Seung-hyun, Roh Jae-won, Jo Yu-ri, and Won Ji-an rounding out the ensemble of colorful characters in the new season.

Watch on Netflix: https://www.netflix.com/title/81203480

About Netflix:
Netflix is one of the world's leading entertainment services, with 278 million paid memberships in over 190 countries enjoying TV series, films and games across a wide variety of genres and languages. Members can play, pause and resume watching as much as they want, anytime, anywhere, and can change their plans at any time.

Squid Game: Season 2 | You’re Invited | Netflix
https://www.youtube.com/@Netflix

Heralding the return of the worldwide hit, a new chapter unfolds as Gi-hun comes back with an agenda, having given up on leaving for the US.

snippet.title: Kehna Galat Galat (Official Video) Javed-Mohsin, Jyoti Nooran | Sana Makbul, Karan Veer M | Kunaal V
snippet.description:
Presenting the official video of "Kehna Galat Galat", a heartfelt recreation of Nusrat Fateh Ali Khan’s timeless melody. The video features Sana Makbul and Karan Veer Mehra in lead roles. This melody has been sung by Jyoti Nooran, composed by the hit duo Javed-Mohsin who brought you Zihaal E Miskin & Pal from the film Jalebi & lyrics penned by Kunaal Vermaa.

snippet.title: Kaffara Episode 69 - [Eng Sub] - Ali Ansari - Laiba Khan - Zoya Nasir - 30th September 2024
snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Kaffara Episode 69 - [Eng Sub] - Ali Ansari - Laiba Khan - Zoya Nasir - 30th September 2024 - HAR PAL GEO

Sitara, a lively orphan living with her brother, aunt, and uncle, finds joy in life's small things despite her aunt's poor treatment. Her aunt keeps her around because she has a share in the family's property.
Salar, the son of a wealthy businessman, is passionate about photography, which often earns him criticism from his family. With a pure heart, Salar is known for evading his responsibilities.
At her cousin's wedding, Sitara wrongly assumes Salar is the photographer. Salar develops a soft spot for Sitara after seeing how poorly she is treated. However, due to a conspiracy, objections arise about their closeness. Salar, once again, avoids the issue, leaving Sitara to face doubts from her own family.
Can Sitara prove she’s not guilty? Will Salar help her avoid further mistreatment? Will her family support Sitara? Can Salar show he genuinely cares? Will there be more plots against Sitara?

7th Sky Entertainment Presentation 
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi 
Director: Muhammad Iftikhar Iffi
Writer: Shafia Khan

snippet.title: Kaffara Episode 70 - [Eng Sub] - Ali Ansari - Laiba Khan - Zoya Nasir - 1st October 2024
snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Kaffara Episode 70 - [Eng Sub] - Ali Ansari - Laiba Khan - Zoya Nasir - 1st October 2024 - HAR PAL GEO

Sitara, a lively orphan living with her brother, aunt, and uncle, finds joy in life's small things despite her aunt's poor treatment. Her aunt keeps her around because she has a share in the family's property.
Salar, the son of a wealthy businessman, is passionate about photography, which often earns him criticism from his family. With a pure heart, Salar is known for evading his responsibilities.
At her cousin's wedding, Sitara wrongly assumes Salar is the photographer. Salar develops a soft spot for Sitara after seeing how poorly she is treated. However, due to a conspiracy, objections arise about their closeness. Salar, once again, avoids the issue, leaving Sitara to face doubts from her own family.
Can Sitara prove she’s not guilty? Will Salar help her avoid further mistreatment? Will her family support Sitara? Can Salar show he genuinely cares? Will there be more plots against Sitara?

7th Sky Entertainment Presentation 
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi

Writer: Shafia Khan

snippet.title: Mystery Cooking Challenge 😂
snippet.description:
Welcome to the "Gareebo Ka Laughter Chefs Challenge" - where cooking meets comedy in the most hilarious way possible! In this uproarious cooking show, our contestants, armed with limited resources and plenty of humor, compete to whip up the wackiest dishes that will leave you in stitches! 🤣👩‍🍳 

Watch as our talented chefs face unexpected challenges, from quirky ingredient swaps to outrageous cooking tasks that will test their creativity and comedic timing. Who will rise to the occasion and claim the title of the ultimate laughter chef? Tune in for non-stop entertainment, mouth-watering dishes, and plenty of laughs!

Don't forget to like, subscribe, and hit the notification bell for more funny cooking challenges and entertaining culinary adventures! Join us for a show filled with laughter, camaraderie, and some unforgettable kitchen mishaps. Get ready to laugh and cook along with us!

snippet.title: 3 Days at BMPS Kochi LAN in ONE Video! | Kaztro Vlogs
snippet.description:
Join me, Kaztro, as I take you through an exhilarating journey at the BMPS Kochi LAN event in this action-packed video! Over the course of three incredible days, we dive into the world of gaming, competition, and community. From intense matches to behind-the-scenes moments, this vlog captures the essence of what makes BMPS Kochi a must-visit for any gaming enthusiast. Watch as I share highlights of thrilling gameplay, meet fellow gamers, and explore the vibrant atmosphere of the LAN event. Whether you're a hardcore gamer or just curious about the gaming scene, this video has something for everyone! Don’t forget to like, comment, and subscribe for more gaming adventures. Let’s relive the excitement together! #BMPSKochi #KaztroVlogs #GamingEvent #LANParty #Esports #GamingCommunity #Vlog #KochiGaming

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

snippet.description:
क्या होता है जब एक बेकसूर पुलिसवाला, एक खूबसूरत पत्रकार और एक गैंगस्टर मिलकर अपराध की दुनिया में मचाते हैं धूम? 😂 अक्षय कुमार और सुनील शेट्टी की धमाकेदार एक्शन के बीच परेश रावल की कॉमेडी आपको हंसने पर मजबूर कर देगी। नसीरुद्दीन शाह का मजेदार अंदाज़ और रज़ा मुराद की गंभीरता के बीच रवीना टंडन की खूबसूरती मसालेदार कॉमेडी का तड़का लगाती है। इस एक्शन थ्रिलर में हंसी का पूरा तड़का मिलेगा। 🤣

What happens when an innocent cop, a beautiful journalist, and a gangster come together to cause chaos in the crime world? 😂 Amidst Akshay Kumar and Suniel Shetty's explosive action, Paresh Rawal's hilarious comedy will make you burst into laughter. Naseeruddin Shah’s quirky character and Raza Murad’s intensity, paired with Raveena Tandon’s charm, create a perfect recipe for comedy. This action thriller is a laughter riot! 🤣

Movie: Mohra (1994)
Cast: Akshay Kumar, Raveena Tandon, Suniel Shetty, Paresh Rawal, Naseeruddin Shah, Raza Murad
Director: Rajiv Rai
Music Director: Viju Shah
Producer: Gulshan Rai

Keywords:

Episode 4203: Gokuldham Society Ki Badnaami
--------------------------------------------------------
The colony members are torn about how to address the scholarship situation, and they're considering being transparent about what really happened. Will they muster the courage to come clean?

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - Ep 4203 | 30 Sep 2024
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab #Latest #New #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2024 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo #16yearsoftmkoc  #4000episodes

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

Click here to watch the episode of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah :

Subscribe to the LIONSGATE: YouTube Channel for the latest movie trailers, clips, and more: https://bit.ly/2Z6nfym

https://www.lionsgate.com/movies/john-wick
https://x.com/JohnWickMovie
https://www.instagram.com/johnwickmovie/
https://www.facebook.com/johnwickmovie/

#JohnWick

People keep asking if he’s back, and yeah–we’re thinking he is.  “John Wick,” the revolutionary first film of the iconic action franchise, roars into theaters on November 3 & 6 for its 10-year anniversary. 

“John Wick” tells the now-legendary story of the retired assassin’s (Keanu Reeves) quest for vengeance after thugs steal his car and kill his puppy, triggering the furious reemergence of the world’s deadliest and most-feared hitman.  

“John Wick” solidified Reeves’ reputation as an action superstar while also beginning a successful franchise of three sequels and a prequel television series.  The film also spawned popular video games and comic books.   

Fans attending the Fathom screenings will be treated to more from the mythic John Wick universe with an exclusive sneak peek at the upcoming “Ballerina,” which expands the world of Wick with the story of Eve Macarro (Ana de Armas), who is beginning her training in the assassin traditions of the Ruska Roma.

snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Kaffara Episode 68 - [Eng Sub] - Ali Ansari - Laiba Khan - Zoya Nasir - 29th September 2024 - HAR PAL GEO

Sitara, a lively orphan living with her brother, aunt, and uncle, finds joy in life's small things despite her aunt's poor treatment. Her aunt keeps her around because she has a share in the family's property.
Salar, the son of a wealthy businessman, is passionate about photography, which often earns him criticism from his family. With a pure heart, Salar is known for evading his responsibilities.
At her cousin's wedding, Sitara wrongly assumes Salar is the photographer. Salar develops a soft spot for Sitara after seeing how poorly she is treated. However, due to a conspiracy, objections arise about their closeness. Salar, once again, avoids the issue, leaving Sitara to face doubts from her own family.
Can Sitara prove she’s not guilty? Will Salar help her avoid further mistreatment? Will her family support Sitara? Can Salar show he genuinely cares? Will there be more plots against Sitara?

7th Sky Entertainment Presentation 
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

snippet.title: CID कैसे खोलेगी Camera में छिपा राज़? | CID | सी.आई.डी. | Latest Episode | 27 Sep 2024
snippet.description:
Click here to Subscribe to LIV Crime: 
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCzXpAx4v6rFLYXkJZ5nmSvQ?sub_confirmation=1

On their journey to Satara, the CID team encounters an injured man who leads them to a startling discovery near a waterfall. As Daya attempts to save Abhijeet, an unexpected incident complicates their mission. With a mysterious camera found at the scene, the team seeks answers from Madan’s wife. Is Madan missing, or is there more to this story than meets the eye? Join us as we unravel the clues in this thrilling investigation.

Show Name: CID 
Show Cast & Characters: 
• Shivaji Satam as ACP Pradyuman
• Dinesh Phadnis as Inspector Fredricks aka Freddy
• Ashutosh Gowariker as Sr. Inspector Virendra
• Dayanand Shetty as Sr. Inspector Daya
• Narendra Gupta as Dr. R. P. Salunkhe
• Aditya Srivastava as Sr. Inspector Abhijeet
• Shraddha Musale as Dr. Tarika
• Ansha Sayed as Sub-Inspector Purvi
Episode: 1008
Producer: Brijendra Pal Singh

#CID #सीआईडी #cid2024  #CrimeThrillers #CrimeMysteries #Mysteries #Horror #LIVCrime #NewCID #Crime #NewCID #LatestCID

About CID:
-----------------
The first thrilling investigative series on Indian Television is today one of the most popular shows on Sony Entertainment Television. Dramatic and absolutely unpredictable, C.I.D. has captivated viewers over the last eleven years and continues to keep audiences glued to their television sets with its thrilling plots and excitement. Also interwoven in its fast-paced plots are the personal challenges that the C.I.D. team faces with non-stop adventure, tremendous pressure, and risk, all in the name of duty. The series consists of hard-core police procedural stories dealing with investigation, detection, and suspense. The protagonists of the serial are an elite group of police officers belonging to the Crime Investigation Department of the police force, led by ACP Pradyuman [played by the dynamic Shivaji Satam]. While the stories are plausible, there is an emphasis on dramatic plotting and technical complexities faced by the police. At every stage, the plot throws up intriguing twists and turns to keep the officers on the move as they track criminals, led by the smallest of clues.

Click here to watch more episodes from 'Mission : Crime Free India' : https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PL0y08jtgaKIXUMiJR1B1sVpxAvRnK2Okg
